TY  - JOUR
AU  - Simon, Leo K.
T1  - Games with Discontinuous Payoffs
PY  - 1987
Y1  - 1987/10/01
DO  - 10.2307/2297483
JO  - The Review of Economic Studies
JA  - Rev Econ Stud
VL  - 54
IS  - 4
SP  - 569
EP  - 597
SN  - 0034-6527
AB  - We prove an equilibrium existence result for a class of games with an infinite number of strategies. Our theorem generalises an earlier result by Dasgupta and Maskin. We also identify conditions under which the limit of pure-strategy equilibria of a sequence of finite games is an equilibrium for the limit game. We apply this result to obtain new existence results for the multi-firm, l-dimensional version of Hotellings's location game. The techniques used suggest a technique for computing such equilibria.
Y2  - 3/25/2024
UR  - https://doi.org/10.2307/2297483
ER  - 



